</poster>
<seg id="47"> the world is filled with lies and frauds in trash short-text messages flying everywhere. buddha said, "if i do not enter hell, who would enter hell," </seg>
<seg id="48"> anyone who does this, then, congratulate him, he can become a buddha sooner. </seg>
<seg id="49"> any human being has a kind personality when he starts his life. </seg>
<seg id="50"> everyone has a sympathetic heart. </seg>
<seg id="51"> now social ethics is going down day by day, and human hearts are not what they were in those old days. </seg>
