<seg id="7"> until yesterday, the government of linyi, led by you, had illegally placed chen guangcheng under house arrest for 165 days. </seg>
<seg id="8"> you collaborated with rogues and the mafia society to put a blind legal citizen in jail illegally for a long time. </seg>
