<seg id="5"> the child of wang peirong was called off by a gate guard when she was making up missed physics lessons at the third middle school of xuzhou on the morning of january 24, 2006. </seg>
<seg id="6"> the guard said to wang peirong's child that three unidentified men had told the gate guard at the third middle school that wang tianjiao, the child of wang peirong, had not gone back home for three days because of discord between her parents. </seg>
<seg id="7"> now her mother was missing, and they were leaders from her mother's work unit, and wanted to enter the third middle school and take away wang peirong's child. </seg>
