<seg id="26"> now the criminal detection unit of the public security bureau of xuzhou city finds out that, on january 24, three men, including leaders of the work unit of the physics institute where wang peirong works, called wang peirong, but could not find her (wang peirong still does not know what for so far). they tried to find wang peirong in a hurry and wanted to look for a teacher of wang peirong's child to ask if wang peirong's child was still in xuzhou or not. </seg>
<seg id="27"> heavy talking topic: why corruption has a lower risk but anti-corruption has a higher cost </seg>
