</hl>
<poster>
<seg id="2"> <poster>  love life, love lu neng </seg>
</poster>
<seg id="3"> the china football association super league is set for some fierce battles. </seg>
<seg id="4"> luneng taishan is getting combat-ready for the new season with the championship in mind. </seg>
<seg id="5"> hot competitions will be triggered between the dalian, shandong and shanghai teams, the three strongest competitors for the championship. </seg>
<seg id="6"> in the end, who will win the championship? </seg>
<seg id="7"> based on an analysis of their strengths, taishan has a very good chance to become champion, but it is by no means a sure thing. </seg>
<seg id="8"> first of all, the new team members have not had long enough to get worked in. </seg>
<seg id="9"> taishan lost at four major events last year. </seg>
<seg id="10"> this year, taishan recruited two players from the national team--li leilei and wang liang. with the addition of two foreign players soon afterwards, it is safe to say that the team will be stronger. </seg>
<seg id="11"> but because the national football team is preparing for matches with palestine and iraq, there no way to say how well the two players from the national team will integrate. </seg>
<seg id="12"> by the time they return to the club, league matches will be set to begin. </seg>
<seg id="13"> that is why integration has become the most significant issue taishan is facing. </seg>
<seg id="14"> in my view, the national-team players can be used as backups in the first few rounds of league matches. </seg>
<seg id="15"> first, team integration can be achieved using the in-game training. </seg>
<seg id="16"> second, the national-team players who have just played group matches with the national team can use the lull to rest up. </seg>
<seg id="17"> after a few rounds, when the "knife is well sharpened', it will not be too late for them to play top spots. </seg>
<seg id="18"> in addition, the defense has some weaknesses. </seg>
<seg id="19"> last year, taishan's fans had some unfavorable things to say about the team's defense. </seg>
<seg id="20"> this year, the defense will have improved with the recruitment of li leilei. but it's still not the time to sit back and relax. </seg>
<seg id="21"> there's still the problem of sluggish turnaround at the center back position, and the substitutes for this position are either too old or lacking in experience. </seg>
<seg id="22"> if performance at the center back position can be stabilized, taishan will gain some momentum on the road to becoming champion. </seg>
<seg id="23"> in my opinion, they might as well use ren yongshun, who is strong physically. although he lacks experience, he should be put to work this year so as to be ready in the future. </seg>
<seg id="24"> in addition, gao yao can play center back as well. </seg>
<seg id="25"> taishan has quite a few players who can play defending midfield, such as cui peng and hai bing. </seg>
<seg id="26"> gao yao is physically very strong and a ferocious interceptor. he should be able to handle the center back position. </seg>
<seg id="27"> another question is whether the foreign recruits can adjust. </seg>
<seg id="28"> taishan has been plagued by problems with foreign recruits. </seg>
<seg id="29"> the performance of daniel [daniel danciulescu] last year was far from stellar. </seg>
<seg id="30"> we know that this year's selection of foreign players has not yet been finalized. </seg>
<seg id="31"> i think that apart from bringing in an excellent striker, a true left-footed midfielder should also be recruited this year. </seg>
<seg id="32"> except for xing rui, who played for the team a few years ago, taishan has not had a true left-footed player with good skills. </seg>
<seg id="33"> although players like cui peng and other can play the position, a truly competent left half back would be greatly preferred to fill-in. </seg>
<seg id="34"> if these three issues can be solved, taishan's road to the championship should be somewhat smoother. </seg>
<seg id="35"> as a shandong football fan, i'm really hoping taishan can win the championship this year. </seg>
<seg id="36"> but to be frank, with things looking like they do in the championships this year, taishan has a good chance, but it is far from a sure thing. </seg>
</DOC>
